cons : (n : ‚Ñ§)(xs : NonZeroList) ‚Üí ¬¨ n ‚â° 0 ‚Üí NonZeroList
cons n (xs , _) _ .fst = n ‚à∑ xs
cons n ([] , _) p .snd = p , tt
